high_descs: Face the fridge in front of you.
Open the fridge in front of you, take a tomato out then close the fridge.
Turn around and face the table in front of you.
Place the tomato on the table in front of you.
Take the silver knife from the table in front of you.
Slice the tomato in front of you.
Place the knife on the table in front of you.
Take a tomato slice from the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the microwave on your right.
Heat up the tomato slice in the microwave in front of you and take it out.
Turn right then face the white table to your right.
Place the warm tomato slice on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm tomato slice on the white table.

high_descs: move back slightly from the fridge in order to open the door
open the fridge door and remove the tomato that is on the right side of the second shelf and close the door
turn around and move forward to the white square table
put the tomato on to the table to the left of the black coffee mug
pick up the knife that is behind the tomato on the table
slice the tomato that is to the left of the black coffee mug with the knife
put the knife on the table on top of the spatula
pick up a tomato slice from the table
turn around and move to the microwave that is on the counter to the left of the fridge
open the microwave door, put the slice of tomato in to the microwave on the plate, close the door, cook for a few second, open the door and remove the tomato slice, close the door
turn around and move back to the white table
put the slice of tomato on to the right side of the table
anns.task_desc: put a cooked slice of tomato on to the table

high_descs: Open the refrigerator door.
Pick up the tomato on the right.  Close the door.
Turn around and walk to the table.
Put the tomato down to the right of the tomato.
Pick up the knife just past the two tomatoes.
Slice the tomato on the right.
Put the knife down on top of the spatula and spoon.
Pick up a slice of the tomato.
Turn right and walk to the middle of the room.  Turn right and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the tomato slice in, turn it on, open the door and remove the tomato slice.
Turn right and walk to the wall next to the refrigerator.  Turn right at the wall and walk to the table.
Put the slice of tomato down to the right of the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Get a tomato out of the refrigerator, slice it, and heat it.
